    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="句子基本組成"><a href="#句子基本組成" class="headerlink" title="句子基本組成"></a>句子基本組成</h1><p><img src="a01.jpg" alt="basic"></p>
<ul>
<li>主詞 Subject<ul>
<li>名詞、代名詞、動名詞、不定詞、從屬連接詞引導子句</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>動詞 Verb<ul>
<li>完全不及物動詞(smile)<ul>
<li>不需受詞</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>不完全不及物動詞(be verb)<ul>
<li>不需受詞，需主詞補語</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>完全及物動詞(play, give)<ul>
<li>需受詞</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>不完全及物動詞(call)<ul>
<li>需受詞跟補語</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>受詞 Object<ul>
<li>及物動詞的對象</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>補語 Complement<ul>
<li>主詞補語、受詞補語</li>
<li>We consider him <u>trustworthy</u>.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>修飾詞 Modifier<ul>
<li>修飾名詞的形容詞</li>
<li>修飾代名詞的形容詞</li>
<li>修飾動詞的副詞</li>
<li>修飾形容詞的副詞</li>
<li>修飾副詞的副詞</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="五大句型"><a href="#五大句型" class="headerlink" title="五大句型"></a>五大句型</h1><ul>
<li>Subject + Verb</li>
<li>Subject + Verb + Subject Complement</li>
<li>Subject + Verb + Object</li>
<li>Subject + Verb + Indirect Object + Direct Object</li>
<li>Subject + Verb + Object + Object Complement</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="片語"><a href="#片語" class="headerlink" title="片語"></a>片語</h1><h2 id="種類"><a href="#種類" class="headerlink" title="種類"></a>種類</h2><ul>
<li>介係詞片語(on the playground)</li>
<li>動名詞片語(taking a walk)</li>
<li>不定詞片語(to form a good habit)</li>
<li>分詞片語(dressed in blue)</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="功能"><a href="#功能" class="headerlink" title="功能"></a>功能</h2><ul>
<li>名詞片語(To give is …)</li>
<li>形容詞片語(The man dressed in blue)<ul>
<li>修飾名詞或當補語</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>副詞片語(Of course)<ul>
<li>修飾動詞、形容詞、子句</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="子句"><a href="#子句" class="headerlink" title="子句"></a>子句</h1><h2 id="種類-1"><a href="#種類-1" class="headerlink" title="種類"></a>種類</h2><ul>
<li>主要子句</li>
<li>從屬子句<ul>
<li>由從屬連接詞引導的子句</li>
<li>需依附在主要子句</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>對等子句<ul>
<li>由對等連接詞連接的子句</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="句子意義上類型"><a href="#句子意義上類型" class="headerlink" title="句子意義上類型"></a>句子意義上類型</h1>]]></content>
    
